title: The Animals - Live In Poughkeepsie,NY 1983 ak320
description:
The Animals - Live In Poughkeepsie,NY 1983 ak320 

Recorded live in Poughkeepsie, NY 1983. The CD cover credits Eric Burdon & The Animals, however these are live tracks by The Original Animals (Burdon, Price, Chandler, Valentine and Steel) recording during their first official re-union tour in 1983.-(Info taken from ericburdonalbums.com). Nice soundboard or FM recording. Liberated boot from the Swingin' Pig label. Set list taken from back cover of the Swingin' Pig art work.

Recorded Live at Unknown Venue, Poughkeepsie, NY,1983.
Excellent Soundboard Recording - CBR 320ak.

Disc 2

02. Heart Attack
03. House Of The Rising Sun
04. Hard Times

06. It's My Life
07. Don't Bring Me Down
08. Young Girls
09. Boom Boom
10. We've Gotta Get Out Of This Place

Personnel: Eric Burdon :: Alan Price :: Chas Chandler :: Hilton Valentine :: John Steel
